  "3314700": {
    "name": "KINTSUGI - A Journey Through The Broken Pieces",
    "steam_appid": 3314700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KINTSUGI 是一款受到中世纪日本修复陶瓷艺术启发的游戏，这种艺术将裂纹转变为装饰元素，并用金色突显其美感。  <br>游戏的目标是像 3D 拼图一样，通过碎片拼接完成破损的器物。这一过程不仅恢复了物品的完整性，同时也反映了金缮哲学，这种哲学将缺陷、无常以及过去的痕迹视为美与价值的来源。</p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这种哲学认为，一个完成的作品象征着重生——一个修复后的物品获得了新的独特性和它之前所没有的故事。它鼓励人们反思自己的生活经历，表明困难和改变并不会削弱我们，反而可能成为我们成长的基础。它还展示了即便在经历了艰难转变的事物中，也可以发现美。</p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中目前有 4 个随机选择的位置，可以放置用来拼接器物的桌子（未来可能会更多）。</p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/e6befa95ab7d21c75343082a5f80d5a0.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/e6befa95ab7d21c75343082a5f80d5a0.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/e6befa95ab7d21c75343082a5f80d5a0.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/05f06fad86605508d6e5f916690cb462.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/05f06fad86605508d6e5f916690cb462.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/05f06fad86605508d6e5f916690cb462.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/138418cb7967a521f0c47f6ea3ad467d.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/138418cb7967a521f0c47f6ea3ad467d.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/138418cb7967a521f0c47f6ea3ad467d.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/74e2124fa2637eb04d28a2ad2f9a79c5.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/74e2124fa2637eb04d28a2ad2f9a79c5.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/74e2124fa2637eb04d28a2ad2f9a79c5.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供了 5 个难度等级：</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>非常简单模式</strong></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/dd4741c104fe6eee3367128858818e46.avif?t=1767548838\" width=146 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/f8bbaafb6a2d6e6df10eadd503f64090.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/f8bbaafb6a2d6e6df10eadd503f64090.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/f8bbaafb6a2d6e6df10eadd503f64090.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那些不适合当前拼接部分的碎片会消失，这消除了猜测哪些碎片适合、哪些不适合的困惑。  <br>此外，拼接非常简单，即使是碎片之间的微小连接也会被检测到，碎片会自动跳到它们的位置。你不需要精确对准；靠近就足够了。  <br>在这个模式中，碎片不会旋转。  <br>碎片只会在此模式中消失。</p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏会将拼接位置移动到关卡中的随机地点。  <br>目前有 4 个（演示版中只有 1 个）。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简单模式</strong></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/78f2020dfd95d6415339eed5c173c318.avif?t=1767548838\" width=142 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/8ac90e6ff2ce0e57f55b8894c9e5ad34.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/8ac90e6ff2ce0e57f55b8894c9e5ad34.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/8ac90e6ff2ce0e57f55b8894c9e5ad34.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，碎片不再消失，“弱连接”也不起作用。碎片必须有坚固的连接才能粘在一起。  <br>碎片不会旋转。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>普通模式</strong></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/44a52d9c89d2904c7659bf473940bf54.avif?t=1767548838\" width=142 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/2b6b703bb8677d6d97fd4505eae259b4.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/2b6b703bb8677d6d97fd4505eae259b4.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/2b6b703bb8677d6d97fd4505eae259b4.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个模式下，碎片现在会随机旋转，但仅限于 3 个轴中的 2 个。此外，它们的旋转以 45 度为单位，因此找到正确的位置并不太难。  <br>碎片只有在正确对齐时才能粘到其余部分上。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>普通+模式</strong></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/2f3ba623ebb95e0e4416715c48f48813.avif?t=1767548838\" width=142 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/beb9b5a1710a65fe6367882d68898605.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/beb9b5a1710a65fe6367882d68898605.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/beb9b5a1710a65fe6367882d68898605.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从现在开始，碎片会平滑地旋转，因此需要更高的精度。  <br><br>需要多精确？ 碎片仍然在 3 个轴中的 2 个上旋转，但只需要 10 度的偏差就能使它们与已经拼接的部分匹配。  <br><br>我对这个游戏很糟糕，所以示例图片有点不完美 ;)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑战模式</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/298d09e72c61cff212ccbe6713805dee.avif?t=1767548838\" width=142 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/586ee95334add786575d4d8976455c6d.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/586ee95334add786575d4d8976455c6d.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/586ee95334add786575d4d8976455c6d.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这与普通+模式相同，但精度要求从 10 度降低到 5 度。  <br>你需要更加精确地对齐碎片。  <br><br>注意！ 这个模式可能会让人感觉游戏在“作弊”或碎片“真的不适合”。它没有作弊，而且“确实有效” <strong>TM</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>给想要感受金缮精神的人</strong></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/100b263c69faec383e8ee7873d82235a.avif?t=1767548838\" width=142 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/3fbd73e3a467d32adcff8798bf599210.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/3fbd73e3a467d32adcff8798bf599210.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/3fbd73e3a467d32adcff8798bf599210.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个最终模式中，碎片会在所有轴上旋转，使得它极具挑战性并考验耐心。这里的精度仍然是 5 度（我没有胆量再减少），并且拼接对“质量”的要求超过了预期。  <br>真的，只有当你“知道”简单的时代已经过去时才玩这个模式 ;)  <br>你需要更仔细地对齐碎片。并且要慢慢来。  <br><br>注意！ 这个模式可能会让你觉得前一个模式是公平的。这个模式也是如此。  <br>我再说一次——它“确实有效” <strong>TM :) </strong></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为什么没有“困难”模式？</p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为真正的金缮艺术是困难的。</p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它需要耐心、精确、时间、深思熟虑、自控能力，以及在破碎的陶瓷中发现美的能力。  <br>就是这样 :)</p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可能有多个用户共享同一台电脑。</strong></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此游戏有 3 个独立的配置文件，每个配置文件允许单独保存游戏进度。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>演示版只有一个配置文件。</strong></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>演示版中的点数可以转移到完整游戏中。</strong></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/65368010f6d14a9ac98c32c40090b611.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/65368010f6d14a9ac98c32c40090b611.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/65368010f6d14a9ac98c32c40090b611.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现在聊聊价格和耐心的回报 :) </h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/95205544306315026a4c2062674ffbb5.poster.avif?t=1767548838\" width=790 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/95205544306315026a4c2062674ffbb5.webm?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314700/extras/95205544306315026a4c2062674ffbb5.mp4?t=1767548838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个器物都有它的“价格”和完成后可以获得的点数。  <br>如果器物的价格高于可用点数，则价格显示为<strong>灰色</strong>。</p>",
